<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>DnD 5e Character Builder</h1>
    <p class="lead">Dungeon and Dragons 5th edition character builder. This is a database that saves character information to an online database for tracking growth of your saved characters. You can create, view, update, and delete characters at your whim while playing in your campaign.</p>
    <p class="text-muted" style="font-size:small">Learn more about Dungeon and Dragons by clicking the button below.</p>
    <p><a href="https://dnd.wizards.com/" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
</div>

